{"tid":1780676,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區諾軒被控大聲公襲警 控方撤回匿名申請 揭露EEE實為高振邦","createTime":"2019-12-12T14:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T16:09:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0e07be2878d0bfa8806cddbe2258fd58fe7c0030","tid":1780676,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191212/large/1576146601_b26c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191212%2Flarge%2F1576146601_b26c.jpg&h=f80a46fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警司高振邦一度被匿名為EEE。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員區諾軒今年7月到油麻地一帶調停警民衝突，其間被指以大聲公襲兩警，其中一人正是主持警方四點鐘發佈會的警司高振邦。案件今日再訊，區諾軒否認控罪。控方撤回將警員匿名的申請，案件定於下月20日開審。區諾軒庭外指，控方今日的做法，證明當初辯方反對警員匿名的堅持有道理，希望本案對其他警員匿名案件有啟迪作用。<br />\n<br />\n案件今在九龍城裁判法院再訊。控罪指被告區諾軒（32歲）於今年7月8日凌晨，在油麻地彌敦道與登打士街及咸美頓街交界，襲擊執行職務的警員23663關志豪及警司高振邦。<br />\n<br />\n區庭外表示不排除會自辯。被問到有否信心脫罪時，他坦言「唔敢講」，但會盡全力說服法庭，他並沒有襲擊警員的意圖。<br />\n<br />\n兩警曾被稱為AAA與EEE<br />\n本案首次提訊時，涉案兩警的姓名分別以AAA及EEE代替。當時控方聲稱，做法是為保障警員證人的私隱，以免對他們出庭作供構成壓力。惟今日控方稱，已向律政司索取意見，經考慮後決定撤回有關警員匿名的申請，但並無進一步解釋原因。<br />\n<br />\n控方今透露，審訊時將會傳召五名證人作供，並會將一些從社交媒體下載的片段呈堂。辯方不反對控方將警方拍攝的兩段影片呈堂，但表示會傳召負責下載新聞片段的警員作供，屆時將爭議有關片段的準確性及完整性。此外，辯方預計會傳召一至兩名證人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，區被指事發時用大聲公推撞警員關志豪的長盾，並在警方防線前用大聲公與警察公共關係科人員溝通，其間因聲浪太大，導致警司高振邦的耳朵感痛楚，惟未有對其聽覺造成永久傷害。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱被襲的警方傳媒聯絡隊負責人、公共關係科警司高振邦，身影經常在衝突現場出現，但屢次拒絕回應記者查問。高亦不時現身警方記者會，但多次囂張打斷記者追問。上月初，六間傳媒代表頭戴標語，抗議警方粗暴對待前線記者，自恃是記招主持的高振邦點名喝令他們離場，隨後更宣佈取消記者會，說畢即轉身入房，記者室亦秒速熄燈「趕客」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191212/60371113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60371113&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc1Df25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=b71a6be0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F60371113&h=54bef863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191212/60371113</a>"},{"pid":"5630abee0b2a2103d90ec9c1ffc9684f28a1c295","tid":1780676,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa00d7de1ba16cc2055ba7edfbef3b570dd46ace","tid":1780676,"uid":207902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868714740e5ca2905f26009dd5c00325da023007","tid":1780676,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa00d7de1ba16cc2055ba7edfbef3b570dd46ace","tid":1780676,"uid":207902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" cl